Scene,Nature/LogFence2,15080,0,0,0,1,0,LogFence2,-4206.187,-1,-141.2234,15.00001,88.71084,-7.071133E-06,0.5,0.5,0.5,Physical,Entities,Default,Default|255/255/255/255,Projection|CategoryName:Nature
/// Logic
component ActivationZoneTrigger
{
Description = "Manage 'Active' state of other objects on enter";
Debug = false;

Global = false;
Ids = "";
IdsTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";
Names = "";
NamesTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";
DeactivateIds = "";
DeactivateIdsTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";
DeactivateNames = "";
DeactivateNamesTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";

ObjectType = "";
ObjectTypeTooltip = "If specified only objects of selected type/types (separated by '|') will trigger component";

_triggered = false;

function OnCollisionStay(obj)
{
if (self._triggered) { return; }

# Filter Object Type
if (self.ObjectType != "" && !String.Split(self.ObjectType, "|").Contains(obj.Type)) { return; }
if (!self.Global && String.Split(self.ObjectType, "|").Contains("Human") && obj.Player != Network.MyPlayer) { return; }

self._triggered = true;
self.ProcessAsync();

if (self.Debug)
{
Game.Debug(self.MapObject.Name + " - ActivationZoneTrigger");
}
}

coroutine ProcessAsync()
{
if (String.Trim(self.Ids) != "")
{
for (id in String.Split(self.Ids, " "))
{
object = Map.FindMapObjectByID(Convert.ToInt(id));
if (object != null) { object.Active = true; }
}
}

if (String.Trim(self.DeactivateIds) != "")
{
for (id in String.Split(self.DeactivateIds, " "))
{
object = Map.FindMapObjectByID(Convert.ToInt(id));
if (object != null) { object.Active = false; }
}
}

if (String.Trim(self.Names) != "")
{
for (name in String.Split(self.Names, " "))
{
objects = Map.FindMapObjectsByName(name);
for (object in objects) { object.Active = true; }
}
}

if (String.Trim(self.DeactivateNames) != "")
{
for (name in String.Split(String.Trim(self.DeactivateNames), " "))
{
objects = Map.FindMapObjectsByName(name);
for (object in objects) { object.Active = false; }
}
}
}
}

component Buildable
{
BuildInteractionRadius = 10.0;
BuildInteractionRadiusTooltip = "Range on interaction. Ignored if object has colliders";
BuildTime = 15.0;
BuildCost = 500;
BuildDelay = 0.1;
BuildEffect = "";
BuildEffectScale = 1.0;
Ids = "";
IdsTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";
Names = "";
NamesTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";
DeactivateIds = "";
DeactivateIdsTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";
DeactivateNames = "";
DeactivateNamesTooltip = "Separated by whitespace";

_keyPressTimer = 0;
_currentTime = 0;
_currentCost = 0;
_inUse = false;
_human = null;
_collidingHuman = null;
_finished = false;

_projectionsState = false;
_projections = List();
_toActivate = List();
_toDeactivate = List();

function Init()
{
if (self.MapObject.GetBoundsCenter() == null) {self.MapObject.AddSphereCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3.Zero, self.BuildInteractionRadius); }
}

function OnGameStart()
{
if (self.Ids != "")
{
for (id in String.Split(self.Ids, " "))
{
object = Map.FindMapObjectByID(Convert.ToInt(id));
if (object != null) { self._toActivate.Add(object); }
}
}

if (self.Names != "")
{
for (name in String.Split(self.Names, " "))
{
objects = Map.FindMapObjectsByName(name);
for (object in objects) { self._toActivate.Add(object); }
}
}

if (self.DeactivateIds != "")
{
for (id in String.Split(self.DeactivateIds, " "))
{
object = Map.FindMapObjectByID(Convert.ToInt(id));
if (object != null) { self._toDeactivate.Add(object); }
}
}

if (self.DeactivateNames != "")
{
for (name in String.Split(self.DeactivateNames, " "))
{
objects = Map.FindMapObjectsByName(name);
for (object in objects) { self._toDeactivate.Add(object); }
}
}

self.SpawnProjections();
}

function SendNetworkStream()
{
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._inUse);
}

function OnNetworkStream()
{
self._inUse = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && !self._inUse && message == "request")
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(sender);
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "t"))
{
self._currentTime = Convert.ToFloat(String.Substring(message, 1));
if (self._currentTime >= self.BuildTime) { self.FinishBuild(); }
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "c"))
{
self._currentCost = Convert.ToInt(String.Substring(message, 1));
}
}

function OnNetworkTransfer(oldOwner, newOwner) 
{
if (newOwner == Network.MasterClient && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
}
elif (newOwner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.StartBuilding();
}
}

function OnPlayerSpawn(player, character)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "t" + Convert.ToString(self._currentTime));
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "c" + Convert.ToString(self._currentCost));
}
}

function OnPlayerLeave(player)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer) 
{
if (player.ID == Network.MyPlayer.ID) 
{
self._human = null;
self._inUse = false;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}
}
}

function OnCharacterDie(victim, killer, killerName)
{
if (victim.Type == "Human" && (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)) 
{
if (victim.Player.ID == Network.MyPlayer.ID) 
{
self._human = null;
self._inUse = false;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}
}
}

function OnCollisionEnter(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine)
{
self.ShowProjections();
}
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine)
{
isEngineer = other.Player.GetCustomProperty("Rank") == "Engineer";
if (!isEngineer)
{
text = "Only Engineer can build this";
}
elif (!self._inUse && self._currentCost < self.BuildCost)
{
text = "Resources " + Convert.ToString(self._currentCost) + "/" + Convert.ToString(self.BuildCost) + ")" + String.Newline;
text += "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to add " + Convert.ToString(Math.Min(100, Main.EngineerResources - Main._resourcesUsed));
text += " or hold to add " + Math.Min(self.BuildCost - self._currentCost, Main.EngineerResources - Main._resourcesUsed);
self._collidingHuman = other;
}
elif (!self._inUse)
{
text = "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to build (" + String.FormatFloat(self.BuildTime - self._currentTime, 1) + " left)";
self._collidingHuman = other;
}
elif (self._inUse && self._human != null)
{
text = "Building (" + String.FormatFloat(self.BuildTime - self._currentTime, 1) + " left)" + String.Newline;
text += "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to stop";
}
elif (self._inUse && self._human == null)
{
text = "Someone is building";
}

UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", text, 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
}
}

function OnCollisionExit(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine)
{
self.ShowProjections();
if (self._inUse && self._human != null) { self.StopBuilding(); }
}
}

function OnFrame()
{
if (!self._inUse && self._collidingHuman != null && self._collidingHuman.Player.GetCustomProperty("Rank") == "Engineer")
{
if (self._currentCost < self.BuildCost)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
self._keyPressTimer = 1.0;
}
elif (Input.GetKeyHold("Interaction/Interact") && self._keyPressTimer <= 0)
{
amount = Math.Min(self.BuildCost - self._currentCost, Main.EngineerResources - Main._resourcesUsed);
self._currentCost += amount;
Main._resourcesUsed += amount;
Main.SetLegend();
Game.Print("Added " + Convert.ToString(amount) + " resources for build");
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("c" + Convert.ToString(self._currentCost));
}
elif (Input.GetKeyUp("Interaction/Interact") && self._keyPressTimer > 0)
{
amount = Math.Min(100, Main.EngineerResources - Main._resourcesUsed); # 100 or as much as player has
self._currentCost += amount;
Main._resourcesUsed += amount;
Main.SetLegend();
Game.Print("Added " + Convert.ToString(amount) + " resources for build");
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("c" + Convert.ToString(self._currentCost));
}
}
elif (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.StartBuilding();
}
else
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "request");
}
}
}
elif (self._inUse && self._human != null && Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
self.StopBuilding();
}
}

function OnTick()
{
if (self._keyPressTimer > 0) { self._keyPressTimer -= Time.TickTime; }
self._collidingHuman = null;

if (self._inUse && self._human != null)
{
self._currentTime += Time.FrameTime;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("t" + Convert.ToString(self._currentTime));
if (self._currentTime >= self.BuildTime) { self.FinishBuild(); }
}
}

function OnSecond()
{
self.ShowProjections();
}

function SpawnProjections()
{
for (object in self._toActivate)
{
projectionComp = object.GetComponent("Projection");
if (projectionComp == null)
{
Game.Debug("Projection component not found on object with id " + Convert.ToString(object.ID));
continue;
}
name = object.Name;
category = projectionComp.GetCategoryName();
position = object.Position;
posText = position.X + "," + position.Y + "," + position.Z;
rotation = object.Rotation;
rotationText = rotation.X + "," + rotation.Y + "," + rotation.Z;
scale = object.Scale;
scaleText = scale.X + "," + scale.Y + "," + scale.Z;

projection = Map.CreateMapObjectRaw("Scene," + category + "/" + name +",0,0,0,0,1,0," + name + "Projection" + "," + posText + "," + rotationText + "," + scaleText 
+ ",None,Entities,Default,Transparent|255/255/255/25|Misc/None|1/1|0/0");
if (projection != null) { self._projections.Add(projection); }
}
}

function StartBuilding()
{
self._human = self._collidingHuman;
self._inUse = true;
}

function StopBuilding()
{
self._human = null;
self._inUse = false;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}

function ShowProjections()
{
if (self._finished) { return; }
if (self._projections.Count == 0) { return; }

currentProjectionState = self._collidingHuman != null;
if (currentProjectionState != self._projectionsState)
{
self._projectionsState = currentProjectionState;
for (object in self._projections) { object.Active = self._projectionsState; }
}
}

function FinishBuild()
{
if (self._finished) { return; }
self._finished = true;
for (object in self._projections) { object.Active = false; }
self.ToggleObjects();
self._human = null;
self._inUse = false;
self.MapObject.Active = false;
}

coroutine ToggleObjects()
{
for (object in self._toDeactivate) { object.Active = false; }
for (object in self._toActivate)
{
object.Active = true;
if (Network.IsMasterClient && self.BuildEffect != "") { Game.SpawnEffect(self.BuildEffect, object.Position, Vector3.Zero, self.BuildEffectScale); }
wait self.BuildDelay;
}
}
}

component Cannon
{
UnlimitedAmmo = false;
MaxAmmo = 10;
Cooldown = 2.0;
ProjectileLiveTime = 5.0;
LimitVerticalRotation = true;
VerticalRotation = 45.0;
LimitHorizontalRotation = false;
HorizontalRotation = 75.0;

_rotateSpeed = 270;
_currentCameraPosition = 0;
_cameraPositions = List();
_ballSpeed = 300.0;
_barrel = null;
_humanMount = null;
_barrelEnd = null;
_inUse = false;
_cooldownLeft = 0.0;
_ammoLeft = 0;
_human = null;
_collidingHuman = null;

_minVerticalRotation = null;
_maxVerticalRotation = null;
_minHorizontalRotation = null;
_maxHorizontalRotation = null;

function Init()
{
self._barrel = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Barrel");
self._barrelEnd = self._barrel.GetTransform("End");
self._humanMount = self.MapObject.GetTransform("HumanMount");
self.MapObject.AddSphereCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3.Zero, 5.0);
self._ammoLeft = self.MaxAmmo;

self._minVerticalRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation.X - self.VerticalRotation;
self._maxVerticalRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation.X + self.VerticalRotation;
self._minHorizontalRotation = self.MapObject.Rotation.Y - self.HorizontalRotation;
self._maxHorizontalRotation = self.MapObject.Rotation.Y + self.HorizontalRotation;

if (self._minVerticalRotation < 0.0) {
self._minVerticalRotation += 360.0;
}
if (self._minHorizontalRotation < 0.0) {
self._minHorizontalRotation += 360.0;
}

if (self._maxVerticalRotation > 360.0) {
self._maxVerticalRotation -= 360.0;
}
if (self._maxHorizontalRotation > 360.0) {
self._maxHorizontalRotation -= 360.0;
}

self._cameraPositions.Add(Vector3(0, 1.5, -15));
self._cameraPositions.Add(Vector3(0, 1, -5));
self._cameraPositions.Add(Vector3(0, 2, -20));
}

function SendNetworkStream()
{
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._barrel.LocalRotation);
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._inUse);
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._ammoLeft);
}

function OnNetworkStream()
{
rotation = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
self._barrel.LocalRotation = rotation;
self._inUse = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
self._ammoLeft = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && !self._inUse && message == "request")
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(sender);
}
}

function OnNetworkTransfer(oldOwner, newOwner) 
{
if (newOwner == Network.MasterClient && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
self.ResetBarrel();
}
elif (newOwner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self._inUse = true;
human = Network.MyPlayer.Character;
if (human != null && human.Type == "Human")
{
human.MountTransform(self._humanMount, Vector3.Zero, Vector3.Zero);
Camera.SetManual(true);
self._human = human;
}
}
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine && !self._inUse)
{
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to use cannon.", 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
}
}

function OnTick()
{
self._collidingHuman = null;
}

function OnFrame()
{
if (self._inUse && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self._cooldownLeft = self._cooldownLeft - Time.FrameTime;
message = "Cooldown: " + Convert.ToString(Convert.ToInt(Math.Clamp(self._cooldownLeft, 0.0, self.Cooldown)));
if (!self.UnlimitedAmmo)
{
message = message + " Ammo: " + Convert.ToString(self._ammoLeft);
}
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", message, 0.1);

barrelRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation;
baseRotation = self.MapObject.Rotation;

if (Input.GetKeyDown("General/ChangeCamera"))
{
self._currentCameraPosition += 1;
self._currentCameraPosition = Math.Mod(self._currentCameraPosition, self._cameraPositions.Count);
}

mouseSpeed = Input.GetMouseSpeed();
baseRotation.Y += mouseSpeed.X * Time.FrameTime * self._rotateSpeed;
barrelRotation.X -= mouseSpeed.Y * Time.FrameTime * self._rotateSpeed;

# Rotation Limits
if (self.LimitHorizontalRotation) {
baseRotation.Y = self.ClampAngle(baseRotation.Y, self._minHorizontalRotation, self._maxHorizontalRotation);
}
if (self.LimitVerticalRotation) {
barrelRotation.X = self.ClampAngle(barrelRotation.X, self._minVerticalRotation, self._maxVerticalRotation);
}

self._barrel.LocalRotation = barrelRotation;
self.MapObject.Rotation = baseRotation;

cameraOffest = self._cameraPositions.Get(self._currentCameraPosition) * self.MapObject.Scale.X;
Camera.SetPosition(self._barrelEnd.Position + self._barrelEnd.Right * (cameraOffest.X + 0.03)
+ self._barrelEnd.Forward * cameraOffest.Z + self._barrelEnd.Up * cameraOffest.Y);
Camera.SetRotation(Vector3(barrelRotation.X, baseRotation.Y, 0));

hasAmmo = self._ammoLeft > 0 || self.UnlimitedAmmo;
if (self._cooldownLeft <= 0.0 && hasAmmo && Input.GetKeyHold("Human/AttackDefault"))
{
self.Fire();
}
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
self._human.Unmount();
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
self._inUse = false;
self.ResetBarrel();
Camera.SetManual(false);
return;
}
}
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && self._inUse)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner.Character == null || self.NetworkView.Owner.Character.Type != "Human" || self.NetworkView.Owner.Character.MountedTransform != self._humanMount)
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
self._inUse = false;
self.ResetBarrel();
Camera.SetManual(false);
return;
}
}
if (!self._inUse && self._collidingHuman != null)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact")) 
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer) 
{
self._inUse = true;
self._collidingHuman.MountTransform(self._humanMount, Vector3.Zero, Vector3.Zero);
Camera.SetManual(true);
self._human = self._collidingHuman;
}
else
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "request");
}
}
}
}

function ResetBarrel()
{
self._barrel.LocalRotation = Vector3(0, 0, 0);
}

function Fire()
{
self._cooldownLeft = self.Cooldown;
self._ammoLeft = self._ammoLeft - 1;
if (self._human != null)
{
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", self._barrelEnd.Position, self.MapObject.Rotation, 0.5);
Game.SpawnProjectileWithOwner("CannonBall", self._barrelEnd.Position, Vector3.Zero, self._barrel.Forward.Normalized * self._ballSpeed, 
Vector3(0, -20, 0), self.ProjectileLiveTime, self._human);
}
}

function ClampAngle(angle, min, max) 
{
if (Math.Abs(min - max) > 180.0) 
{
if (angle > max && angle < min) 
{
if (Math.Abs(angle - max) > Math.Abs(angle - min)) { return min; } 
else { return max; }
} 
return angle;
} 
else 
{
if (angle < min) { return min; }
elif (angle > max) { return max; }
return angle;
}
}
}

component CannonWagon
{
MoveForce = 20.0;
JumpForceScale = 1.3;
MaxMoveSpeed = 50.0;
RotateSpeed = 3.0;

_inUse = false;
_horse = null;
_human = null;
_collidingHuman = null;
_collidingDrive = false;
_rigidbody = null;
_healthComponent = null;
_leftWheel = null;
_rightWheel = null;
_cannon = null;
_jumpCoolDown = 0;

UnlimitedAmmo = false;
MaxAmmo = 10;
Cooldown = 2.0;
ProjectileLiveTime = 5.0;
LimitVerticalRotation = true;
VerticalRotation = 45.0;
LimitHorizontalRotation = false;
HorizontalRotation = 75.0;

IsSettingsMaster = false;
SettingsTag = "";

_rotateSpeed = 270;
_currentCameraPosition = 0;
_cameraPositions = List();
_ballSpeed = 300.0;
_barrel = null;
_humanMount = null;
_barrelEnd = null;
_cooldownLeft = 0.0;
_ammoLeft = 0;
_collidingCannon = false;
_inUseCannon = false;
_cannonIsUsed = "";
_targetBarrelRotation = null;
_targetBaseRotation = null;
_hasRotateCannon = false;
_rotationSyncCoolDdown = 0;

_minVerticalRotation = null;
_maxVerticalRotation = null;
_minHorizontalRotation = null;
_maxHorizontalRotation = null;

function Init()
{
self._horse = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Horse");
self.MapObject.AddSphereCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3.Zero, 5.5);
self._rigidbody = self.MapObject.GetComponent("Rigidbody");
self._healthComponent = self.MapObject.GetComponent("DestroyableObject");
self._leftWheel = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Carriage/Wheels/LeftWheelPivot");
self._rightWheel = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Carriage/Wheels/RightWheelPivot");
self.AddCannon();

self._barrel = self._cannon.GetTransform("Barrel");
self._barrelEnd = self._barrel.GetTransform("End");
self._humanMount = self._cannon.GetTransform("HumanMount");
self._ammoLeft = self.MaxAmmo;

self._minVerticalRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation.X - self.VerticalRotation;
self._maxVerticalRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation.X + self.VerticalRotation;
self._minHorizontalRotation = self.MapObject.Rotation.Y - self.HorizontalRotation;
self._maxHorizontalRotation = self.MapObject.Rotation.Y + self.HorizontalRotation;

if (self._minVerticalRotation < 0.0) {
self._minVerticalRotation += 360.0;
}
if (self._minHorizontalRotation < 0.0) {
self._minHorizontalRotation += 360.0;
}

if (self._maxVerticalRotation > 360.0) {
self._maxVerticalRotation -= 360.0;
}
if (self._maxHorizontalRotation > 360.0) {
self._maxHorizontalRotation -= 360.0;
}

self._cameraPositions.Add(Vector3(0, 1.5, -15));
self._cameraPositions.Add(Vector3(0, 1.5, -5));
self._cameraPositions.Add(Vector3(0, 2, -20));
}

function OnGameStart()
{
if (!self.IsSettingsMaster) { return; }
for (object in Map.FindMapObjectsByComponent("CannonWagon"))
{
comp = object.GetComponent("CannonWagon");
if (comp.SettingsTag != self.SettingsTag) { continue; }
comp.MoveForce = self.MoveForce;
comp.JumpForceScale = comp.JumpForceScale;
comp.MaxMoveSpeed = self.MaxMoveSpeed;
comp.RotateSpeed = self.RotateSpeed;

comp.UnlimitedAmmo = self.UnlimitedAmmo;
comp.MaxAmmo = self.MaxAmmo;
comp._ammoLeft = comp.MaxAmmo;
comp.Cooldown = self.Cooldown;
comp.ProjectileLiveTime = self.ProjectileLiveTime;
comp.LimitVerticalRotation = self.LimitVerticalRotation;
comp.VerticalRotation = self.VerticalRotation;
comp.LimitHorizontalRotation = self.LimitHorizontalRotation;
comp.HorizontalRotation = self.HorizontalRotation;

rigidbody = object.GetComponent("Rigidbody");
rigidbody.Gravity = self._rigidbody.Gravity;
}
}

function SendNetworkStream()
{
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._targetBarrelRotation);
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._targetBaseRotation);
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._cannonIsUsed);
}

function OnNetworkStream()
{
self._targetBarrelRotation = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
self._targetBaseRotation = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
self._cannonIsUsed = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
}

function AddCannon()
{
if (self._cannon == null)
{
position = self.MapObject.Position;
x = position.X;
y = position.Y + 2.5;
z = position.Z + -1.2;

result = Physics.LineCast(Vector3(x,y,z), Vector3(x,y-100,z), "MapObjects");
if (result != null)
{
y = result.Point.Y + 0.2;
}

pos = x + "," + y + "," + z;
self._cannon = Map.CreateMapObjectRaw("Scene,Interact/Cannon3,0,0,1,0,1,0,WagonCannon,"+ pos +",0,0,0,0.35,0.35,0.35,None,Characters,Default,Default|255/255/255/255");
self._cannon.Parent = self.MapObject;
self._cannon.Forward = self.MapObject.Forward;
}
}

function SetAmmoCount(amount)
{
self._ammoLeft = amount;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("a" + Convert.ToString(self._ammoLeft));
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && !self._inUse && message == "request")
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(sender);
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "a"))
{
self._ammoLeft = Convert.ToInt(String.Substring(message, 1));
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "c"))
{
self._cannonIsUsed = String.Substring(message, 1);
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "r") && (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer))
{

vals = String.Split(String.Substring(message, 1), ",");
#Game.Print("message " + vals);
rot = Vector3(Convert.ToFloat(vals.Get(0)), Convert.ToFloat(vals.Get(1)),Convert.ToFloat(vals.Get(2)));
self._targetBarrelRotation = rot;
rot = Vector3(Convert.ToFloat(vals.Get(3)), Convert.ToFloat(vals.Get(4)),Convert.ToFloat(vals.Get(5)));
self._targetBaseRotation = rot;
}
}

function OnNetworkTransfer(oldOwner, newOwner) 
{
if (newOwner == Network.MasterClient && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
}
elif (newOwner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self._inUse = true;
human = Network.MyPlayer.Character;
if (human != null && human.Type == "Human")
{
human.MountTransform(self._horse, Vector3(0, 1.95, 0), Vector3.Zero);
human.ClearHooks();
self._human = human;
}
}
}

function OnPlayerLeave(player)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && Convert.ToString(player.ID) == self._cannonIsUsed)
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "c");
}
}

function OnPlayerSpawn(player, character)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "a" + Convert.ToString(self._ammoLeft));
}
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine)
{
diff = (other.Position - self.MapObject.Position);
project = Vector3.Project(diff, self.MapObject.Forward);
if (project.Magnitude > 1 * self.MapObject.Scale.Z && project.Normalized == self.MapObject.Forward)
{
if (!self._inUse && !other.IsMounted)
{
text = "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to drive wagon.";
if (self._healthComponent != null) { text += " (" + Convert.ToString(self._healthComponent.GetHealth()) + "HP)"; }
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", text, 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
self._collidingDrive = true;
}
}
else
{
if (!self._inUseCannon && self._cannonIsUsed == "" && !other.IsMounted)
{
text = "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to use cannon.";
if (self._healthComponent != null) { text += " (" + Convert.ToString(self._healthComponent.GetHealth()) + "HP)"; }
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", text, 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
self._collidingCannon = true;
}
}
}
}

function OnTick()
{
self._collidingHuman = null;
self._collidingDrive = false;
self._collidingCannon = false;

if (self._jumpCoolDown > 0) { self._jumpCoolDown -= Time.TickTime; }

if (self._leftWheel != null && self._rightWheel != null)
{
L = Vector3.Distance(self._leftWheel.Position, self._rightWheel.Position);
r = self._leftWheel.Scale.Y / 2;

localVelocity = self.MapObject.Transform.InverseTransformDirection(self._rigidbody.GetVelocity());
angularVelocity = self._rigidbody.GetAngularVelocity();

v_x = localVelocity.Z;
omega = angularVelocity.Y;

leftWheelRotationSpeed = (v_x - (L / 2) * omega) / r;
rightWheelRotationSpeed = (v_x + (L / 2) * omega) / r;

leftWheelRotation = leftWheelRotationSpeed * Time.TickTime * Math.Rad2DegConstant * 0.3; # Character moves too fast for irl physics
rightWheelRotation = rightWheelRotationSpeed * Time.TickTime * Math.Rad2DegConstant * 0.3;

self._leftWheel.Rotate(Vector3(leftWheelRotation, 0, 0));
self._rightWheel.Rotate(Vector3(rightWheelRotation, 0, 0));
}

if (self._inUseCannon)
{
if (self._human != Network.MyPlayer.Character || (self._human != null && self._human.MountedTransform != self._humanMount))
{
self._inUseCannon = false;
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "c");
Camera.SetManual(false);
return;
}
if (self._rotationSyncCoolDdown <= 0 && self._hasRotateCannon)
{
barrelRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation;
baseRotation = self._cannon.Rotation;
rotationMessage = barrelRotation.X + "," + barrelRotation.Y + "," + barrelRotation.Z;
rotationMessage += "," + baseRotation.X + "," + baseRotation.Y + "," + baseRotation.Z;
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "r" + rotationMessage);
self._hasRotateCannon = false;
self._rotationSyncCoolDdown = 0.5;
}
}        
else
{
if (self._targetBarrelRotation != null)
{
start = Quaternion.FromEuler(self._barrel.LocalRotation);
targetBarrelRotation = Quaternion.FromEuler(self._targetBarrelRotation);
maxStep = self._rotateSpeed * 0.02;
newBarrelRotation = Quaternion.RotateTowards(start, targetBarrelRotation, maxStep);
self._barrel.LocalRotation = newBarrelRotation.Euler;
# Game.Print("barrel From "+ start + " To " + newBarrelRotation);
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && newBarrelRotation == targetBarrelRotation)
{
self._targetBarrelRotation = null;
# Game.Print("targetBarrelRotation set to none");
}
}
if (self._targetBaseRotation != null)
{
start = Quaternion.FromEuler(self._cannon.Rotation);
maxStep = self._rotateSpeed * 0.02;
targetBaseRotation = Quaternion.FromEuler(self._targetBaseRotation);
newBaseRotation = Quaternion.RotateTowards(start, targetBaseRotation, maxStep);
# Game.Print("cannonbase From "+ start + " To " + newBaseRotation);
self._cannon.Rotation = newBaseRotation.Euler;
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && newBaseRotation == targetBaseRotation)
{
self._targetBaseRotation = null;
# Game.Print("targetBaseRotation set to none");
}
}
}

if (self.NetworkView.Owner != Network.MyPlayer) { return; }

if (self._inUse && self._human != null)
{
if (self._human.HasTargetDirection)
{
self.MapObject.Forward = Vector3.Lerp(self.MapObject.Forward, self._human.TargetDirection, self.RotateSpeed * Time.FrameTime);
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Forward * self.MoveForce); 

}
else
{
self.SlowToStop();
}
self.LimitSpeed();
}
}

function OnFrame()
{
self.AnimateHorse();

dismountVelocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
dismountVelocity.Y += 12.0;
if (self._rotationSyncCoolDdown > 0)
{
self._rotationSyncCoolDdown -= Time.FrameTime;
if (self._rotationSyncCoolDdown < 0)
{
self._rotationSyncCoolDdown = 0;
}
}
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
if (self._inUse)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HorseJump") && self._jumpCoolDown <= 0 
&& Physics.LineCast(self.MapObject.Position, self.MapObject.Position - Vector3.Up * 5.0, "MapObjects") != null)
{
self._jumpCoolDown = 1;
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Up * self.JumpForceScale * self._rigidbody.Gravity.Y * -1);
}

if (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1)
{
self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_run");
}
else
{
self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_idle");
}
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookLeft") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookRight") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/Jump"))
{
self._human.Velocity = dismountVelocity;
self._human.Unmount();
self._human = null;
Camera.SetManual(false);
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
self._inUse = false;
return;
}
if (self.NetworkView.Owner.Character == null || self.NetworkView.Owner.Character.Type != "Human" || self.NetworkView.Owner.Character.MountedTransform != self._horse)
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
self._inUse = false;
return;
}
}
else
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
if (velocity.Magnitude < 1)
{
self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(Vector3.Up * velocity.Y);
}
else
{
self._rigidbody.AddForce(-0.5 * velocity.Normalized * velocity.Magnitude);
}
}
}
if (self._inUseCannon && self._human == Network.MyPlayer.Character)
{
self._cooldownLeft = self._cooldownLeft - Time.FrameTime;
message = "Cooldown: " + Convert.ToString(Convert.ToInt(Math.Clamp(self._cooldownLeft, 0.0, self.Cooldown)));
if (!self.UnlimitedAmmo)
{
message = message + " Ammo: " + Convert.ToString(self._ammoLeft);
}
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", message, 0.1);

barrelRotation = self._barrel.LocalRotation;
baseRotation = self._cannon.Rotation;

if (Input.GetKeyDown("General/ChangeCamera"))
{
self._currentCameraPosition += 1;
self._currentCameraPosition = Math.Mod(self._currentCameraPosition, self._cameraPositions.Count);
}

mouseSpeed = Input.GetMouseSpeed();
baseRotation.Y += mouseSpeed.X * Time.FrameTime * self._rotateSpeed;
barrelRotation.X -= mouseSpeed.Y * Time.FrameTime * self._rotateSpeed;

# Rotation Limits
if (self.LimitHorizontalRotation) {
baseRotation.Y = self.ClampAngle(baseRotation.Y, self._minHorizontalRotation, self._maxHorizontalRotation);
}
if (self.LimitVerticalRotation) {
barrelRotation.X = self.ClampAngle(barrelRotation.X, self._minVerticalRotation, self._maxVerticalRotation);
}

self._barrel.LocalRotation = barrelRotation;
self._cannon.Rotation = baseRotation;
self._hasRotateCannon = true;

cameraOffest = self._cameraPositions.Get(self._currentCameraPosition) * self._cannon.Scale.X;
Camera.SetPosition(self._barrelEnd.Position + self._barrelEnd.Right * (cameraOffest.X + 0.01)
+ self._barrelEnd.Forward * cameraOffest.Z + self._barrelEnd.Up * cameraOffest.Y);
Camera.SetRotation(Vector3(barrelRotation.X, baseRotation.Y, 0));

hasAmmo = self._ammoLeft > 0 || self.UnlimitedAmmo;
if (self._cooldownLeft <= 0.0 && hasAmmo && Input.GetKeyHold("Human/AttackDefault"))
{
self.Fire();
}
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/Jump"))
{
self._inUseCannon = false;
self._human.Velocity = dismountVelocity;
self._human.Unmount();
self._human = null;
Camera.SetManual(false);
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "c");
return;
}
}
elif (self._collidingHuman != null)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
if (self._collidingDrive && !self._inUse && !self._collidingHuman.IsMounted)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer) 
{
self._inUse = true;
self._collidingHuman.MountTransform(self._horse, Vector3(0, 1.95, 0), Vector3.Zero);
self._collidingHuman.ClearHooks();
self._human = self._collidingHuman;
}
else
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "request");
}
}
elif (self._collidingCannon && !self._inUseCannon && self._cannonIsUsed == ""  && !self._collidingHuman.IsMounted)
{
self._inUseCannon = true;
self._human = self._collidingHuman;
Camera.SetManual(true);
self._collidingHuman.MountTransform(self._humanMount, Vector3.Zero, Vector3.Zero);
self._collidingHuman.ClearHooks();
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "c" + Convert.ToString(Network.MyPlayer.ID));
}
}
}
}

function SlowToStop()
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity.Y = 0;

if (velocity.Magnitude < 1) { self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(Vector3.Up * velocityY); }
else { self._rigidbody.AddForce(-0.5 * velocity + velocityY * Vector3.Up); }
}

function LimitSpeed()
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity.Y = 0;
velocity = velocity.Normalized * Math.Min(velocity.Magnitude, self.MaxMoveSpeed);
velocity.Y = velocityY;
self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(velocity);
}

function AnimateRider() 
{
if (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1) { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_run");}
else { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_idle"); }
}

function AnimateHorse()
{
if (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1)
{
self._horse.PlayAnimation("horse_Run");
self.MapObject.GetTransform("RunSound").PlaySound();
self.MapObject.GetTransform("Dust").ToggleParticle(true);
}
else
{
self._horse.PlayAnimation("horse_idle0");
self.MapObject.GetTransform("RunSound").StopSound();
self.MapObject.GetTransform("Dust").ToggleParticle(false);
}
}

function Fire()
{
self._cooldownLeft = self.Cooldown;
self._ammoLeft -= 1;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("a" + Convert.ToString(self._ammoLeft));
if (self._human != null)
{
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", self._barrelEnd.Position, self.MapObject.Rotation, 0.5);
Game.SpawnProjectileWithOwner("CannonBall", self._barrelEnd.Position, Vector3.Zero, self._barrel.Forward.Normalized * self._ballSpeed, 
Vector3(0, -20, 0), self.ProjectileLiveTime, self._human);
}
}

function ClampAngle(angle, min, max) 
{
if (Math.Abs(min - max) > 180.0) 
{
if (angle > max && angle < min) 
{
if (Math.Abs(angle - max) > Math.Abs(angle - min)) { return min; } 
else { return max; }
} 
return angle;
} 
else 
{
if (angle < min) { return min; }
elif (angle > max) { return max; }
return angle;
}
}
}

component ColossalTitan
{       
ColossalDamage = 69000;
ColossalHealth = 20000;

ExplosionForceFalloffRange = 1000.0;
ExplosionForceMaxRange = 2000.0;
LightNames = "";
Ids = "";
Names = "";
DeactivateNames = "";

ObjectType = "";
ObjectTypeTooltip = "If specified only objects of selected type/types (separated by '|') will trigger component";

_triggered = false;

function OnCollisionStay(obj)
{
if (self._triggered) { return; }

# Filter Object Type
if (self.ObjectType != "" && !String.Split(self.ObjectType, "|").Contains(obj.Type)) { return; }

self._triggered = true;
self.ColTimer();
}

coroutine ColTimer()
{   
Time.TimeScale = 0.5;
self.ActivateIds(self.Ids, true);
wait 9.0;
self.ActivateNames(self.LightNames, true);
self.ActivateNames(self.Names, true);
self.ActivateNames(self.DeactivateNames, false);
if (Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self.SpawnFX();
self.SpawnCol();
}
wait 2.0;
myCharacter = Network.MyPlayer.Character;
if (myCharacter != null)
{
pos = Vector3(-1742,684,11835.1);
distance = Vector3.Distance(pos, myCharacter.Position);
scale = 1;
direction = myCharacter.Position - pos;
direction.Y = 0;

if (distance <= self.ExplosionForceMaxRange)
{
if (distance > self.ExplosionForceFalloffRange) {
scale -= (distance - self.ExplosionForceFalloffRange) / self.ExplosionForceFalloffRange;
}

if (myCharacter.IsMounted) { myCharacter.Unmount(); } #TODO - check if this breaks mounts
myCharacter.AddForce(direction.Normalized * scale * 300.0 + Vector3.Up * 50.0, "Impulse");
}
}
wait 4.0;
Time.TimeScale = 1;
wait 3.0;
self.ActivateNames(self.LightNames, false);
}

function ActivateIds(ids, enable)
{
if (String.Trim(ids) != "")
{
for (id in String.Split(ids, " "))
{
object = Map.FindMapObjectByID(Convert.ToInt(id));
if (object != null) { object.Active = enable; }
}
}
}

function ActivateNames(names, enable)
{
if (String.Trim(names) != "")
{
for (name in String.Split(names, " "))
{
objects = Map.FindMapObjectsByName(name);
for (object in objects) { object.Active = enable; }
}
}
}

coroutine SpawnFX()
{
pos = Vector3(-1742,684,11835.1);
posf = Vector3(-1742,2434,11835.1);
posog = Vector3(-1742,436,11835.1); 
pose = Vector3(-1742,684,11835.1);
for (i in Range(0, 70, 1))
{   
yOffset = 100 + (25 * i);

Game.SpawnEffect("Boom5", pos + Vector3(0, yOffset, 0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 25.0);
}
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf, Vector3(90, 0, 0), 30.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,25,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 30.0);

Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,225,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 70.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom5", posf + Vector3(0,225,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 200.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,250,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 65.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,275,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 60.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,285,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 55.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,295,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 50.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,305,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 45.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,315,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 40.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,325,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 35.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,335,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 30.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,345,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 25.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,355,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 20.0);
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom2", posf + Vector3(0,365,0), Vector3(90, 0, 0), 15.0);
for(i in Range(0, 100, 1))
{   
fxrad = 700 - (7 * i);
Game.SpawnEffect("ShifterThunder", pose, Vector3.Zero, 150 + fxrad);
}

wait 0.8;
for(i in Range(0, 15, 1))
{
wait 0.25;
radius = 25 + (20 * i);

Game.SpawnEffect("Boom6", posog, Vector3(90, 0, 0), 25.0 + radius);
}
}

coroutine SpawnCol()
{   pos = Vector3(-1742,684,11835.1);
wait 2.1;
self.newShifter(self.ColossalHealth,false,"Normal",30,self.ColossalDamage,250,pos);
}

function newShifter(health,realShifter,type,size,damage,explotionRadius,position)
{
if (realShifter == false)
{
TITAN = Game.SpawnTitanAt(type, position);
if (TITAN != null)
{
Game.SpawnEffect("ShifterThunder", TITAN.Position, Vector3.Zero, explotionRadius * 2.0);
TITAN.Size = size;
TITAN.MaxHealth = health;
TITAN.Health = health;
TITAN.CustomDamageEnabled = true;
TITAN.CustomDamage = damage;
TITAN.Reveal(5);

TITAN.WalkSpeedBase = 7;
TITAN.RotateSpeed = 2.0;
TITAN.AttackWait = 0.7;
TITAN.AttackPause = 0.9;
TITAN.ActionPause = 0.9;
TITAN.AttackSpeedMultiplier = 0.4;
TITAN.TurnSpeed = 1.0;
TITAN.DetectRange = 5000;
TITAN.TurnPause = 0.2;
}
}
if (realShifter == true)
{
TITAN = Game.SpawnShifter(type);
if (TITAN != null)
{
TITAN.MaxHealth = health;
TITAN.Health = health;
TITAN.CustomDamageEnabled = true;
TITAN.CustomDamage = damage;
}
}
}
}

component DestroyableObject
{
MaxHealth = 300;
Team = "Human";
DamageEffect = "";
DamageEffectScale = 1.0;
DeathEffect = "";
DeathEffectScale = 1.0;
InvincibleTime = 3.0;

IsSettingsMaster = false;
SettingsTag = "";

_currentHealth = 0;
_invincibleTimer = 0;

function Init()
{
self.MapObject.AddBoxCollider("Region", "Hitboxes");
self._currentHealth = self.MaxHealth;
}

function OnGameStart()
{
if (!self.IsSettingsMaster) { return; }
for (object in Map.FindMapObjectsByComponent("DestroyableObject"))
{
comp = object.GetComponent("DestroyableObject");
if (comp.SettingsTag != self.SettingsTag) { continue; }
comp.MaxHealth = self.MaxHealth;
comp._currentHealth = comp.MaxHealth;
comp.Team = self.Team;
comp.DamageEffect = self.DamageEffect;
comp.DamageEffectScale = self.DamageEffectScale;
comp.DeathEffect = self.DeathEffect;
comp.DeathEffectScale = self.DeathEffectScale;
comp.InvincibleTime = self.InvincibleTime;
}
}

function GetMaxHealth() { return self.MaxHealth; }
function GetHealth() { return self._currentHealth; }

function SetHealth(amount) 
{
self._currentHealth = amount;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("h" + Convert.ToString(self._currentHealth));

if (self._currentHealth > 0 ) { self.MapObject.Active = true; }
else { self.MapObject.Active = false; }
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (String.StartsWith(message, "h"))
{
newHealth = Convert.ToInt(String.Substring(message, 1));
if (newHealth < self._currentHealth) { self._invincibleTimer = self.InvincibleTime; }
self._currentHealth = newHealth;

if (self._currentHealth > 0 ) { self.MapObject.Active = true; }
else { self.MapObject.Active = false; }
}
}

function OnPlayerJoin(player)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient) { self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "h" + Convert.ToString(self._currentHealth)); }
}

function OnPlayerSpawn(player, character)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient) { self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "h" + Convert.ToString(self._currentHealth)); }
}

function OnGetHit(character, name, damage, type)
{
if (!Network.IsMasterClient || self._invincibleTimer > 0 || character.Type == self.Team) { return; }

self._currentHealth -= damage;
self._invincibleTimer = self.InvincibleTime;

if (self._currentHealth <= 0 && self.DeathEffect != "")
{
Game.SpawnEffect(self.DeathEffect, self.MapObject.Position, Vector3.Zero, self.DeathEffectScale);
}
elif (self.DamageEffect != "")
{
Game.SpawnEffect(self.DamageEffect, self.MapObject.Position, Vector3.Zero, self.DamageEffectScale);
}

self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("h" + Convert.ToString(self._currentHealth));
if (self._currentHealth > 0 ) { self.MapObject.Active = true; }
else { self.MapObject.Active = false; }
}

function OnTick()
{
if (self._invincibleTimer > 0) { self._invincibleTimer -= Time.TickTime; }
}
}

component Destructible
{
function Init()
{            
self.MapObject.AddSphereCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3.Zero, 10.0);
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{                
if (other.Type == "Titan" || other.Type == "Shifter")
{
if ( self.MapObject != null )
{
Game.SpawnEffect("Boom1", self.MapObject.Position, Vector3.Zero, 1);
Map.DestroyMapObject(self.MapObject, true);
}
return;
}
}
}

component Executioner
{
Description = "Makes Executioner1 and Executioner2 useable by players.";
KillRadius = 20.0;
_currentHuman = null;
_moving = false;
_dropping = false;
_log = null;
_startPosition = Vector3(0,0,0);
_endTransform = null;
_dropSpeed = 50.0;
_riseSpeed = 10.0;
_pauseTime = 3.0;
_pauseTimeLeft = 0.0;
_radius = null;

function Init()
{
self.MapObject.AddBoxCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3(0, 120, 0), Vector3(80, 50, 80));
self._log = self.MapObject.GetTransform("ExecutionerLog1");
self._startPosition = self._log.Position;
self._endTransform = self._log.GetTransform("End");
self._radius = self.KillRadius * self.MapObject.Scale.Z;
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (message == "request" && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
if (!self._moving)
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessageAll("drop");
}
}
if (message == "drop" && sender == Network.MasterClient)
{
self.Drop();
}
}

function Drop()
{
self._dropping = true;
self._moving = true;
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine)
{
self._currentHuman = other;
if (self._dropping || self._moving) { UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Executioner is in motion", 0.1); }
else { UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to use executioner", 0.1); }
}
}

function OnTick()
{
self._currentHuman = null;
if (self._moving && self._dropping && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
for (titan in Game.Titans)
{
if (titan.Health > 0 && Vector3.Distance(self._endTransform.Position, titan.Position) < self._radius)
{
titan.GetKilled("Executioner");
}
}
}

if (self._moving)
{
currentPosition = self._log.LocalPosition;
if (self._dropping)
{
currentPosition.Y = currentPosition.Y - self._dropSpeed * Time.FrameTime;
if (currentPosition.Y <= 50)
{
currentPosition.Y = 50;
self._dropping = false;
self._pauseTimeLeft = self._pauseTime;
}
}
else
{
if (self._pauseTimeLeft >= 0)
{
self._pauseTimeLeft = self._pauseTimeLeft - Time.FrameTime;
}
else
{
currentPosition.Y = currentPosition.Y + self._riseSpeed * Time.FrameTime;
if (currentPosition.Y >= 120)
{
currentPosition.Y = 120;
self._moving = false;
}
}
}
self._log.LocalPosition = currentPosition;
}
}

function OnFrame()
{
if (self._currentHuman != null)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(Network.MasterClient, "request");
}
}
}
}

component HorseMount
{
MaxGallopSpeed = 45.0;
MaxRunSpeed = 65.0;
GallopMoveForce = 45.0;
RunMoveForce = 65.0;
JumpForceScale = 1.3;
RotateSpeed = 3.8;
JumpForceScaleTooltip = "Jump force is calculated based on gravity and scale provided";
RunStaminaCost = 10.0;
JumpStaminaCost = 25.0;
CanHavePassenger = true;

IsSettingsMaster = false;
SettingsTag = "";

_MaxCallTime = 120.0;
_FollowDistance = 20.0;
_InteractionRange = 3.0;
_MaxStamina = 100.0;
_StaminaRegenDelay = 1.0;

# Synced Stream
_inUse = false;
_isCalled = false;
# Synced Messages
_ownerId = -1;
_hasPassenger = false;

_owner = null;
_horse = null;
_rigidbody = null;
_healthComponent = null;

_human = null;
_collidingRide = null;
_collidingPassenger = null;
_isFollowing = false;
_isPassenger = false;
_callTimeRemaining = 0;
_jumpCooldown = 0;
_isRunning = false;
_currentStamina = 0;
_staminaRegenCooldown = 0;

_isRequestingMount = false;
_isRequestingCall = false;

_HorseProperty = "HorseProperty";

function Init()
{
self.MapObject.AddSphereCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3.Zero, self._InteractionRange);
self._horse = self.MapObject.Transform;
self._rigidbody = self.MapObject.GetComponent("Rigidbody");
self._healthComponent = self.MapObject.GetComponent("DestroyableObject");
self._currentStamina = self._MaxStamina;
}

function OnGameStart()
{
if (!self.IsSettingsMaster) { return; }
for (object in Map.FindMapObjectsByComponent("HorseMount"))
{
comp = object.GetComponent("HorseMount");
if (comp.SettingsTag != self.SettingsTag) { continue; }
comp.MaxGallopSpeed = self.MaxGallopSpeed;
comp.MaxRunSpeed = self.MaxRunSpeed;
comp.GallopMoveForce = self.GallopMoveForce;
comp.RunMoveForce = self.RunMoveForce;
comp.JumpForceScale = self.JumpForceScale;
comp.RunStaminaCost = self.RunStaminaCost;
comp.JumpStaminaCost = self.JumpStaminaCost;
comp.RotateSpeed = self.RotateSpeed;
comp.CanHavePassenger = self.CanHavePassenger;

rigidbody = object.GetComponent("Rigidbody");
rigidbody.Gravity = self._rigidbody.Gravity;
}
}

function OnPlayerSpawn(player, character)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient) 
{ 
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "o" + Convert.ToString(self._ownerId)); 
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "p" + Convert.ToString(self._hasPassenger)); 
}
}

function OnPlayerLeave(player)
{
if (player.ID == self._ownerId)
{
self._ownerId = -1;
self._owner = null;
}

if (player.ID == Network.MyPlayer.ID)
{
if (self._isPassenger)
{
self.SetHasPassenger(false);
self._isPassenger = false;
}
elif(self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer || Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}
}
}

function OnCharacterDie(victim, killer, killerName)
{
if (victim.Type != "Human") { return; }
if (victim.Player.ID == self._ownerId)
{
self._ownerId = -1;
self._owner = null;
}

if (victim.Player.ID == Network.MyPlayer.ID)
{
if (self._isPassenger)
{
self.SetHasPassenger(false);
self._isPassenger = false;
}
elif(self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer || Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}
}
}

function SendNetworkStream()
{
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._inUse);
self.NetworkView.SendStream(self._isCalled);
}

function OnNetworkStream()
{
self._inUse = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
self._isCalled = self.NetworkView.ReceiveStream();
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (String.StartsWith(message, "o"))
{
self._ownerId = Convert.ToInt(String.Substring(message, 1));
if (self._ownerId == -1) { self._owner = null; }
else
{
for (player in Network.Players)
{
if (player.ID == self._ownerId) { self._owner = player; break; }
}  
}
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "p"))
{
self._hasPassenger = Convert.ToBool(String.Substring(message, 1));
}
elif (message == "request" && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && !self._isCalled)
{
if (self._inUse && self._human != null && self._ownerId == sender.ID)
{
self.DismountHorse(false);
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "*You hear someone whistle for your mount..", 1.5);
}
self.NetworkView.Transfer(sender);
}
}

function OnNetworkTransfer(oldOwner, newOwner) 
{
if (self._isRequestingMount) 
{
self._isRequestingMount = false;
self.MountHorse(self._collidingRide);
}
elif (self._isRequestingCall) 
{
self._isRequestingCall = false;
self.Whistle();
}
elif (newOwner == Network.MasterClient && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
self._isCalled = false;
}
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMainCharacter && !other.IsMounted) 
{
project = Vector3.Project(other.Position - self.MapObject.Position, self.MapObject.Forward);
isCollidingRide = project.Normalized == self.MapObject.Forward;
text = "";
if (self._isCalled) { text += "Horse is following it's owner"; }
elif (!self._inUse && (isCollidingRide || !self.CanHavePassenger)) { text += "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to ride"; }
elif (!self._hasPassenger && (!isCollidingRide && self.CanHavePassenger)) {text += "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to ride as passenger"; }
else { return; }

if (self._healthComponent != null) { text += " (" + Convert.ToString(self._healthComponent.GetHealth()) + "HP)"; }

if (self._ownerId != -1 && self._owner != null) 
{
text += " (Owner: " + UI.WrapStyleTag("[" + self._ownerId + "]", "color", "orange") + self._owner.Name + ")";
text += String.Newline;

if (!self._inUse && self._ownerId == Network.MyPlayer.ID && !self._isCalled)
{
text += "Follow [" + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact2") + "]  Unclaim [" + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact3") + "]";
}
}

UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", text, 0.1);
if (isCollidingRide || !self.CanHavePassenger) { self._collidingRide = other; }
elif (self.CanHavePassenger) { self._collidingPassenger = other; }
if (RoomData.GetProperty(self._HorseProperty, null) == null) { RoomData.SetProperty(self._HorseProperty, self.MapObject.ID); }
}
}

function OnTick()
{
myCharacter = Network.MyPlayer.Character;

self._collidingRide = null;
self._collidingPassenger = null;
if (RoomData.GetProperty(self._HorseProperty, null) != null && RoomData.GetProperty(self._HorseProperty, null) == self.MapObject.ID) 
{ RoomData.SetProperty(self._HorseProperty, null); }

if (self._callTimeRemaining > 0) { self._callTimeRemaining -= Time.TickTime; }
if (self._jumpCooldown > 0) { self._jumpCooldown -= Time.TickTime; }
if (self._staminaRegenCooldown > 0) { self._staminaRegenCooldown -= Time.TickTime; }

if (self._staminaRegenCooldown <= 0 && !self._isRunning && self._currentStamina < self._MaxStamina) 
{ 
self._currentStamina += 20.0 * Time.TickTime; 
if (self._currentStamina > self._MaxStamina) { self._currentStamina = self._MaxStamina; }
}

if (myCharacter != null && myCharacter.Type == "Human" && myCharacter.IsMounted && myCharacter.MountedTransform == self._horse 
&& (self._human == null || !self.MapObject.Active))
{
myCharacter.Unmount(); # Prevent stuck players
}

if (self.NetworkView.Owner != Network.MyPlayer) { return; }

if (self._inUse && !self._isPassenger && self._human != null)
{
if (self._human.HasTargetDirection)
{
self.MapObject.Forward = Vector3.Lerp(self.MapObject.Forward, self._human.TargetDirection, self.RotateSpeed * Time.FrameTime);
if (self._isRunning)
{
self._currentStamina -= self.RunStaminaCost * Time.TickTime;
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Forward * self.RunMoveForce);
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Running", 0.2);
self._staminaRegenCooldown = self._StaminaRegenDelay;
}
else
{
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Forward * self.GallopMoveForce); 
}
}
else
{
self.SlowToStop();
}
self.LimitSpeed();
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Stamina: " + String.FormatFloat(Math.Max(0, self._currentStamina / self._MaxStamina * 100.0), 0) + "%" , 0.1);
}
elif (myCharacter != null && myCharacter.Type == "Human" && self._isCalled)
{
myPosition = myCharacter.Position;
myPosition.Y = self.MapObject.Position.Y; # Ignore height in distance check
distanceToOwner = Vector3.Distance(self.MapObject.Position, myPosition);

if (self._isFollowing && distanceToOwner < self._FollowDistance) 
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity *= 0.2;
velocity.Y = velocityY;

self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(velocity);
return; 
}

if (!self._isFollowing && (self._callTimeRemaining <= 0 || distanceToOwner < 10)) 
{
if (self._callTimeRemaining <= 0)
{
self.SetOwnerId(-1);
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "*Your horse couldn't reach you and got lost..", 1.5);
}
else
{
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "*Your horse came to you..", 1.5);
}

velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();

self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(velocity * 0.2);
self._isCalled = false;
self.MapObject.GetTransform("CrazySound").PlaySound();

self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
return;
}

directionToPlayer = (myCharacter.Position - self.MapObject.Position).Normalized;
directionToPlayer.Y = 0;

self.MapObject.Forward = directionToPlayer;
self._rigidbody.AddForce(directionToPlayer * self.GallopMoveForce * 1.5);
self.LimitSpeed();
}

if (!self._inUse && !self._isCalled && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer) { self.SlowToStop(); }

if (self._human != null && (!self._human.IsMounted || self._human.MountedTransform != self._horse))
{
self._human = null;
if (self._isPassenger)
{
self.SetHasPassenger(false);
self._isPassenger = false;
}
else
{
self._inUse = false;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}
}
}

function OnFrame()
{
if (self._human != null) { self.AnimateRider(); }
self.AnimateHorse();

self._isRunning = Input.GetKeyHold("Human/HorseWalk") && self._currentStamina > 0;

if (self._inUse && !self._isPassenger && self._human != null && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer) 
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HorseJump") && self._jumpCooldown <= 0 && self._currentStamina > self.JumpStaminaCost 
&& Physics.LineCast(self.MapObject.Position, self.MapObject.Position - Vector3.Up * 5.0, "MapObjects") != null)
{
self._jumpCooldown = 1;
self._currentStamina -= self.JumpStaminaCost;
self._staminaRegenCooldown = self._StaminaRegenDelay;
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Up * self.JumpForceScale * self._rigidbody.Gravity.Y * -1);
}
elif ((Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HorseMount") 
|| Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookLeft") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookRight"))) 
{
self.DismountHorse(true);
}
}
elif (self._hasPassenger && self._isPassenger && self._human != null 
&& (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HorseMount")))
{
self.SetHasPassenger(false);
self._human.Unmount();
self._human = null;
self._isPassenger = false;
}
elif (!self._inUse && !self._isCalled && self._collidingRide != null && !self._collidingRide.IsMounted && Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.MountHorse(self._collidingRide);
}
else
{
self._isRequestingMount = true;
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "request");
}
}
elif (!self._hasPassenger && !self._isCalled && self._collidingPassenger != null && !self._collidingPassenger.IsMounted && Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
self.SetHasPassenger(true);
self._human = self._collidingPassenger;
self._human.ClearHooks();
self._human.MountTransform(self._horse, Vector3(0, 1.95, -0.4), Vector3.Zero);
self._isPassenger = true;
}
elif ((!self._isCalled || self._isFollowing) && self._human == null && self._ownerId == Network.MyPlayer.ID 
&& (RoomData.GetProperty(self._HorseProperty, null) == null || RoomData.GetProperty(self._HorseProperty, null) == self.MapObject.ID) 
&& Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact2"))
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.Whistle();
}
else
{
self._isRequestingCall = true;
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "request");
}
}
elif (!self._inUse && !self._isCalled && (self._collidingRide != null || self._collidingPassenger != null) 
&& self._ownerId == Network.MyPlayer.ID && Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact3"))
{
self.SetOwnerId(-1);
self.MapObject.GetTransform("Idle3Sound").PlaySound();
}
}

function DismountHorse(transfer) {
self.MapObject.GetTransform("Idle2Sound").PlaySound();

dismountVelocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
dismountVelocity.Y += 12.0;

self._human.Unmount();
self._human.Velocity = dismountVelocity;
self._human = null;
self._inUse = false;
if (transfer)
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
}
}

function MountHorse(human)
{
if (human == null || human.IsMounted) {
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
return;
}

self.MapObject.GetTransform("Idle2Sound").PlaySound();

self._human = human;
self._inUse = true;
self._isCalled = false;

self._human.ClearHooks();
self._human.MountTransform(self._horse, Vector3(0, 1.95, 0.1), Vector3.Zero);

if (self._ownerId == -1)
{
self.SetOwnerId(self._human.Player.ID);
}
}

function Whistle()
{
self._callTimeRemaining = self._MaxCallTime;
self._isCalled = true;
self._inUse = false;

Network.MyPlayer.Character.Emote("Eat");

if (!self._isFollowing && (self._collidingRide != null || self._collidingPassenger != null))
{
self._isFollowing = true;
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "*Whistle!*" + String.Newline + "*You order your horse to follow..", 1.5);
}
else
{
self._isFollowing = false;
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "*Whistle!*" + String.Newline + "*You call for your horse..", 1.5);
}

self.MapObject.GetTransform("CrazySound").PlaySound();
}

function AnimateRider() {
if (self._isPassenger) { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_idle"); }
elif (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1) { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_run");}
else { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_idle"); }
}

function AnimateHorse()
{
if (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1) { self._horse.PlayAnimation("horse_Run"); }
else { self._horse.PlayAnimation("horse_idle0"); }
}

function SlowToStop()
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity.Y = 0;

if (velocity.Magnitude < 1) { self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(Vector3.Up * velocityY); }
else { self._rigidbody.AddForce(-0.5 * velocity + velocityY * Vector3.Up); }
}

function LimitSpeed()
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity.Y = 0;

if (self._isRunning && velocity.Magnitude > self.MaxRunSpeed)
{
velocity = Vector3.Lerp(velocity, velocity.Normalized * self.MaxRunSpeed, 0.1);
}
elif(!self._isRunning && velocity.Magnitude > self.MaxGallopSpeed)
{
velocity = Vector3.Lerp(velocity, velocity.Normalized * self.MaxGallopSpeed, 0.1);
}
#velocity = velocity.Normalized * Math.Min(velocity.Magnitude, self.MaxMoveSpeed);
velocity.Y = velocityY;
self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(velocity);
}

function SetOwnerId(value)
{
self._ownerId = value;

if (self._ownerId == -1) { self._owner = null; }
else
{
for (player in Network.Players)
{
if (player.ID == self._ownerId) { self._owner = player; break; }
}  
}
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("o" + Convert.ToString(self._ownerId));
}

function SetHasPassenger(value)
{
self._hasPassenger = value;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("p" + Convert.ToString(self._hasPassenger));
}
}

component Interior
{
Description = "Used inside buildings and houses.";

function OnCollisionEnter(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMainCharacter && other.IsMine)
{
other.IsInvincible = true;
Camera.FollowDistance = 0.6;
}
}

function OnCollisionExit(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMainCharacter && other.IsMine)
{
other.InvincibleTimeLeft = 2.0;
Camera.ResetDistance();
}
}
}

component ObjectMover
{
Velocity = 10.0;
Direction = "Right";
DirectionDropbox = "Right, Forward";

function OnTick()
{
if (!self.MapObject.Active) { return; }
if (self.Direction == "Right")
{
self.MapObject.Position += self.MapObject.Right * self.Velocity * Time.TickTime;
}
elif (self.Direction == "Forward")
{ 
self.MapObject.Position += self.MapObject.Forward * self.Velocity * Time.TickTime;
}
}
}

component Projection
{
CategoryName = "";

function GetCategoryName() { return self.CategoryName; }
}

component Repairable
{
Cost = 200;
HealthRestored = 100;

_healthComp = null;

function Init()
{
self._healthComp = self.MapObject.GetComponent("DestroyableObject");
if (self._healthComp == null) { Game.Debug("Repairable requires health component, not found at " + Convert.ToString(self.MapObject.ID)); }
}

function GetCost() { return self.Cost; }
function GetHealthRestored() { return self.HealthRestored; }

function CanRepair() 
{
if (self._healthComp == null) { return false; }
maxHealth = self._healthComp.GetMaxHealth();
currentHealth = self._healthComp.GetHealth();
if (maxHealth == currentHealth) { return false; }
return true;
}

function Fix()
{
if (self._healthComp == null) { return false; }
maxHealth = self._healthComp.GetMaxHealth();
currentHealth = self._healthComp.GetHealth();
if (maxHealth == currentHealth) { return false; }
self._healthComp.SetHealth(Math.Min(currentHealth + self.HealthRestored, maxHealth));
return true;
}
}

component TitanSpawnForward
{
Description = "Spawns titans in a area with custom types, health and size.";

Shape = "Square";
TitanCount = 5;
StartActive = true;
TitanTypes = "Default";
SpawnCenter = Vector3(0,0,0);
rangemin = 800;
rangemax = 3500;
Yoffset = 150;
DestroyEffect = "";
DestroyEffectScale = 1.0;
DestroyChildren = true;
_disable = false;
TitanTypesTooltip = "Custom types allowed for this region, separate each type by /. Leave in blank to disable";
ShapeDropbox = "Circle, Square";
fakerChance = 0.05;
dummyChance = 0.05;
stalkerChance = 0.05;
defenderChance = 0.05;

_allowedTypes = List();
_difficultyMultiplier = 1.0;

function Init()
{
if (self.TitanTypes != "")
{
argTypes = String.Split(self.TitanTypes, "/");
for (type in argTypes)
{
self._allowedTypes.Add(type);
}
}
}

function SetDifficultyMultiplier(multiplier)
{
self._difficultyMultiplier = multiplier;
}

function OnCollisionEnter(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human")
{
if (self.StartActive && Network.IsMasterClient && !self._disable)
{
self.SpawnSeveralTitans(Math.Round(self.TitanCount * self._difficultyMultiplier));

if (self.DestroyEffect != "")
{
Game.SpawnEffect(self.DestroyEffect, self.MapObject.Position, self.MapObject.Rotation + Vector3(-90, 0, 0), self.DestroyEffectScale);
}
}
self._disable = true;
}
}

coroutine SpawnSeveralTitans(TitanCount){
while(TitanCount > 0)
{
self.SpawnTitan();
TitanCount -= 1;
}
wait(2.0);
if(self._disable)
{
Map.DestroyMapObject(self.MapObject, self.DestroyChildren);
}
}

function SpawnTitan()
{
spawnPos = Vector3();
if (self.Shape == "Square")
{
radius = Random.RandomInt(self.rangemin, self.rangemax);
angle = Random.RandomFloat(0.0, 1.0) * 360;
pos = self.SpawnCenter;
pos.X =  pos.X + Math.Cos(angle) * radius;
pos.Y =  pos.Y + self.Yoffset;
pos.Z =  pos.Z + Math.Sin(angle) * radius;
spawnPos = pos;
}
elif (self.Shape == "Circle")
{
radius = Random.RandomInt(self.rangemin, self.rangemax);
dir = Random.RandomDirection();
dir.Y = 0;
spawnPos = self.SpawnCenter + dir.Normalized * radius + Vector3.Up * self.Yoffset;
}

type = "Default";
if (self._allowedTypes.Count > 0)
{
type = self._allowedTypes.Get(Random.RandomInt(0, self._allowedTypes.Count));
}

chanceResult = Random.RandomFloat(0, 1);
titan = null;
if (chanceResult < self.fakerChance)
{
titan = Game.SpawnTitanAt("Punk", spawnPos);
titan.DetectRange = 1100;
titan.CanRun = false;
Main.AddSpecialTitan(titan);
}
elif (chanceResult < self.fakerChance + self.dummyChance)
{
titan = Game.SpawnTitanAt("Dummy", spawnPos);
titan.DetectRange = 1100;
Main.AddSpecialTitan(titan);
}
elif (chanceResult < self.fakerChance + self.dummyChance + self.stalkerChance)
{
titan = Game.SpawnTitanAt("Abnormal", spawnPos);
titan.DetectRange = 1100;
titan.FocusRange = 9999;
titan.FocusTime = 9999;
Main.AddSpecialTitan(titan);
}
elif (chanceResult < self.fakerChance + self.dummyChance + self.stalkerChance + self.defenderChance)
{
titan = Game.SpawnTitanAt("Normal", spawnPos);
titan.DetectRange = 60.0;
titan.FocusRange = 120.0;
titan.FocusTime = 3.0;
Main.AddSpecialTitan(titan);
}
else
{
titan = Game.SpawnTitanAt(type, spawnPos);
}
}
}

component Wagon
{
MoveForce = 17.0;
MaxMoveSpeed = 50.0;
RotateSpeed = 2.5;
JumpForceScale = 1.3;
CanSupply = true;
InfiniteSupply = false;
MaxSupplyTimes = 40;

IsSettingsMaster = false;
SettingsTag = "";

_inUse = false;
_riding = false;
_horse = null;
_human = null;
_collidingHuman = null;
_collidingDrive = false;
_collidingRide = false;
_collidingGas = false;
_rigidbody = null;
_healthComponent = null;
_leftWheel = null;
_rightWheel = null;
_leftSitTransform = null;
_rightSitTransform = null;
_supplyTimesLeft = 0;
_jumpCoolDown = 0;

function Init()
{
self._horse = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Horse");
self.MapObject.AddSphereCollider("Region", "Characters", Vector3.Zero, 5.5);
self._rigidbody = self.MapObject.GetComponent("Rigidbody");
self._healthComponent = self.MapObject.GetComponent("DestroyableObject");
self._leftWheel = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Carriage/Wheels/LeftWheelPivot");
self._rightWheel = self.MapObject.GetTransform("Carriage/Wheels/RightWheelPivot");
self._leftSitTransform = self.MapObject.GetTransform("SitRegionBottomLeft");
self._rightSitTransform = self.MapObject.GetTransform("SitRegionBottomRight");
self._supplyTimesLeft = self.MaxSupplyTimes;
}

function OnGameStart()
{
if (!self.IsSettingsMaster) { return; }
for (object in Map.FindMapObjectsByComponent("Wagon"))
{
comp = object.GetComponent("Wagon");
if (comp.SettingsTag != self.SettingsTag) { continue; }
comp.MoveForce = self.MoveForce;
comp.MaxMoveSpeed = self.MaxMoveSpeed;
comp.RotateSpeed = self.RotateSpeed;
comp.JumpForceScale = self.JumpForceScale;
comp.CanSupply = self.CanSupply;
comp.InfiniteSupply = self.InfiniteSupply;
comp.MaxSupplyTimes = self.MaxSupplyTimes;
comp._supplyTimesLeft = comp.MaxSupplyTimes;

rigidbody = object.GetComponent("Rigidbody");
rigidbody.Gravity = self._rigidbody.Gravity;
}
}

function OnNetworkMessage(sender, message)
{
if (Network.IsMasterClient && self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer && !self._inUse && message == "request")
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(sender);
}
elif (String.StartsWith(message, "s"))
{
self._supplyTimesLeft = Convert.ToInt(String.Substring(message, 1));
}
}

function OnPlayerSpawn(player, character)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(player, "s" + Convert.ToString(self._supplyTimesLeft));
}
}

function UseSupply()
{
self._supplyTimesLeft = self._supplyTimesLeft - 1;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("s" + Convert.ToString(self._supplyTimesLeft));
}

function SetSupplyCount(amount)
{
self._supplyTimesLeft = amount;
self.NetworkView.SendMessageOthers("s" + Convert.ToString(self._supplyTimesLeft));
}

function OnNetworkTransfer(oldOwner, newOwner) 
{
if (newOwner == Network.MasterClient && Network.IsMasterClient)
{
self._inUse = false;
}
elif (newOwner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
self._inUse = true;
human = Network.MyPlayer.Character;
if (human != null && human.Type == "Human")
{
human.MountTransform(self._horse, Vector3(0, 1.95, 0), Vector3.Zero);
human.ClearHooks();
self._human = human;
}
}
}

function OnCollisionStay(other)
{
if (other.Type == "Human" && other.IsMine)
{
diff = (other.Position - self.MapObject.Position);
project = Vector3.Project(diff, self.MapObject.Forward);
if (project.Magnitude > 3 * self.MapObject.Scale.Z && project.Normalized == self.MapObject.Forward)
{
if (!self._inUse && !self._riding && !other.IsMounted)
{
text = "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to drive wagon.";
if (self._healthComponent != null) { text += " (" + Convert.ToString(self._healthComponent.GetHealth()) + "HP)"; }
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", text, 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
self._collidingDrive = true;
}
}
elif (project.Magnitude > 4 * self.MapObject.Scale.Z && project.Normalized == self.MapObject.Forward * -1.0)
{
if (!self._inUse && !self._riding && self.CanSupply && !other.IsMounted)
{
if (self.InfiniteSupply)
{
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to refill.", 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
self._collidingGas = true;
}
else
{
left = Math.Max(self._supplyTimesLeft, 0);
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to refill (" + Convert.ToString(self._supplyTimesLeft) + " left.)", 0.1);
if (left > 0)
{
self._collidingHuman = other;
self._collidingGas = true;
}
}
}
}
else
{
if (!self._riding && !other.IsMounted)
{
text = "Press " + Input.GetKeyName("Interaction/Interact") + " to ride wagon.";
if (self._healthComponent != null) { text += " (" + Convert.ToString(self._healthComponent.GetHealth()) + "HP)"; }
UI.SetLabelForTime("MiddleCenter", text, 0.1);
self._collidingHuman = other;
self._collidingRide = true;
}
}
}
}

function OnTick()
{
self._collidingHuman = null;
self._collidingDrive = false;
self._collidingRide = false;
self._collidingGas = false;

if (self._jumpCoolDown > 0) { self._jumpCoolDown -= Time.TickTime; }

if (self._leftWheel != null && self._rightWheel != null)
{
L = Vector3.Distance(self._leftWheel.Position, self._rightWheel.Position);
r = self._leftWheel.Scale.Y / 2;

localVelocity = self.MapObject.Transform.InverseTransformDirection(self._rigidbody.GetVelocity());
angularVelocity = self._rigidbody.GetAngularVelocity();

v_x = localVelocity.Z;
omega = angularVelocity.Y;

leftWheelRotationSpeed = (v_x - (L / 2) * omega) / r;
rightWheelRotationSpeed = (v_x + (L / 2) * omega) / r;

leftWheelRotation = leftWheelRotationSpeed * Time.TickTime * Math.Rad2DegConstant * 0.3; # Character moves too fast for irl physics
rightWheelRotation = rightWheelRotationSpeed * Time.TickTime * Math.Rad2DegConstant * 0.3;

self._leftWheel.Rotate(Vector3(leftWheelRotation, 0, 0));
self._rightWheel.Rotate(Vector3(rightWheelRotation, 0, 0));
}

if (self.NetworkView.Owner != Network.MyPlayer) { return; }

if (self._inUse && self._human != null)
{
if (self._human.HasTargetDirection)
{
self.MapObject.Forward = Vector3.Lerp(self.MapObject.Forward, self._human.TargetDirection, self.RotateSpeed * Time.FrameTime);
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Forward * self.MoveForce); 

}
else
{
self.SlowToStop();
}
self.LimitSpeed();
}
}

function OnFrame()
{   
if (self._human != null) { self.AnimateRider(); }
self.AnimateHorse();

dismountVelocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
dismountVelocity.Y += 12.0;

if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer)
{
if (self._inUse)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HorseJump") && self._jumpCoolDown <= 0 
&& Physics.LineCast(self.MapObject.Position, self.MapObject.Position - Vector3.Up * 5.0, "MapObjects") != null)
{
self._jumpCoolDown = 1;
self._rigidbody.AddForce(self.MapObject.Up * self.JumpForceScale * self._rigidbody.Gravity.Y * -1);
}
elif (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookLeft") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookRight") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/Jump"))
{
self._human.Velocity = dismountVelocity;
self._human.Unmount();
self._human = null;
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
self._inUse = false;
return;
}

if (self.NetworkView.Owner.Character == null || self.NetworkView.Owner.Character.Type != "Human" || self.NetworkView.Owner.Character.MountedTransform != self._horse)
{
self.NetworkView.Transfer(Network.MasterClient);
self._inUse = false;
return;
}
}
}
if (self._riding)
{
if (self._human == null || self._human.MountedMapObject != self.MapObject)
{
self._riding = false;
return;
}
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookLeft") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/HookRight") || Input.GetKeyDown("Human/Jump"))
{
self._human.Velocity = dismountVelocity;
self._human.Unmount();
self._human = null;
self._riding = false;
}
else
{
self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_idle");
}
}
if (self._collidingHuman != null)
{
if (Input.GetKeyDown("Interaction/Interact"))
{
if (self._collidingDrive && !self._collidingHuman.IsMounted && !self._inUse)
{
if (self.NetworkView.Owner == Network.MyPlayer) 
{
self._inUse = true;
self._collidingHuman.MountTransform(self._horse, Vector3(0, 1.95, 0), Vector3.Zero);
self._collidingHuman.ClearHooks();
self._human = self._collidingHuman;
}
else
{
self.NetworkView.SendMessage(self.NetworkView.Owner, "request");
}
}
elif (self._collidingGas && !self._inUse)
{
if (self._collidingHuman.Refill(true))
{
self.UseSupply();
}
}
elif (self._collidingRide && !self._collidingHuman.IsMounted && !self._riding)
{
self._riding = true;
self._human = self._collidingHuman;
posA = self._leftSitTransform.LocalPosition; # Vector3(-1.0, 1.78, -3.5);
posB = self._rightSitTransform.LocalPosition; # Vector3(1.0, 1.78, 1.0);
self._human.MountMapObject(self.MapObject, Random.RandomVector3(posA, posB), Vector3(0, 0, 0));
self._human.ClearHooks();
}
}
}
}

function SlowToStop()
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity.Y = 0;

if (velocity.Magnitude < 1) { self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(Vector3.Up * velocityY); }
else { self._rigidbody.AddForce(-0.5 * velocity + velocityY * Vector3.Up); }
}

function LimitSpeed()
{
velocity = self._rigidbody.GetVelocity();
velocityY = velocity.Y;
velocity.Y = 0;
velocity = velocity.Normalized * Math.Min(velocity.Magnitude, self.MaxMoveSpeed);
velocity.Y = velocityY;
self._rigidbody.SetVelocity(velocity);
}

function AnimateRider() 
{
if (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1) { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_run");}
else { self._human.PlayAnimation("Armature|horse_idle"); }
}

function AnimateHorse()
{
if (self._rigidbody.GetVelocity().Magnitude > 1)
{
self._horse.PlayAnimation("horse_Run");
self.MapObject.GetTransform("RunSound").PlaySound();
self.MapObject.GetTransform("Dust").ToggleParticle(true);
}
else
{
self._horse.PlayAnimation("horse_idle0");
self.MapObject.GetTransform("RunSound").StopSound();
self.MapObject.GetTransform("Dust").ToggleParticle(false);
}
}
}

component ZoneTrigger
{
Description = "Sends specified message when object triggers event";
ObjectType = "";
ObjectTypeTooltip = "If specified only objects of selected type/types (separated by '|') will trigger component";
MessageReciever = "MasterClient";
MessageRecieverDropbox = "MasterClient, Everyone, Others, Player";
MessageRecieverTooltip = "Who recieves message";
TriggerType = "OnEnter";
TriggerTypeDropbox = "OnEnter, OnExit, OnStay";
TriggerTypeTooltip = "Event to trigger sending message";
TriggerAmount = "Once";
TriggerAmountDropbox = "Once, OncePerPlayer, Everytime";
TriggerAmountTooltip = "How many times to trigger";
Message = "";

_triggered = false;

function OnCollisionEnter(obj)
{
if (self.TriggerType == "OnEnter") { self.ProcessTrigger(obj); }
}

function OnCollisionExit(obj)
{
if (self.TriggerType == "OnExit") { self.ProcessTrigger(obj); }
}

function OnCollistionStay(obj)
{
if (self.TriggerType == "OnStay") { self.ProcessTrigger(obj); }
}

function ProcessTrigger(obj)
{
# Trigger Amount
if (self.TriggerAmount == "Once" && !Network.IsMasterClient) { return; }
if (self.TriggerAmount == "Once" && Network.IsMasterClient && self._triggered) { return; }
if (self.TriggerAmount == "OncePerPlayer" && obj.Type != "Human") { return; }
if (self.TriggerAmount == "OncePerPlayer" && obj.Player != Network.MyPlayer) { return; }
if (self.TriggerAmount == "OncePerPlayer" && self._triggered) { return; }

# Filter Object Type
if (self.ObjectType != "" && !String.Split(self.ObjectType, "|").Contains(obj.Type)) { return; }

# Message selected reciever
if (self.MessageReciever == "MasterClient") { Network.SendMessage(Network.MasterClient, "@" + self.Message);}
elif (self.MessageReciever == "Player") { Network.SendMessage(obj.Player, "@" + self.Message);}
elif (self.MessageReciever == "Everyone") { Network.SendMessageAll("@" + self.Message);}
elif (self.MessageReciever == "Others") { Network.SendMessageOthers("@" + self.Message);}

# Trigger Amount
if (self.TriggerAmount == "Once" || (self.TriggerAmount == "OncePerPlayer" && obj.Player == Network.MyPlayer)) { self._triggered = true; }
}
}

extension Utility
{
function WallDistance(position, forward, maxDistance)
{
distance = maxDistance;
wallCast = Physics.LineCast(position, position + forward * distance, "MapObjects");
if (wallCast != null)
{
distance = wallCast.Distance;
}
return distance;
}

function CastToGround(position, forward, groundMaxDifference, maxAngle)
{
pos = position;
up = Vector3.Up;
groundCast = Physics.LineCast(pos + Vector3.Up * groundMaxDifference, pos + Vector3.Down * groundMaxDifference, "MapObjects");
if (groundCast != null && Vector3.Angle(Vector3.Up, groundCast.Normal) <= maxAngle)
{
pos = groundCast.Point;
up = groundCast.Normal;
}
list = List();
list.Add(pos);
list.Add(QuaternionX.LookRotationY(forward, up).Euler);
return list;
}
}
